	<meta property="og:title" content="The Storm Over the University | John R. Searle" />
	<meta property="og:description" content="1. I cannot recall a time when American education was not in a &quot;crisis.&quot; We have lived through Sputnik (when we were &quot;falling behind the Russians&quot;)," />
